类分层结构

        • org.springframework.http.server.reactive.UndertowServerHttpResponse (implements org.springframework.http.ZeroCopyHttpOutputMessage)

      • org.springframework.http.server.reactive.RxNettyServerHttpResponse
    • org.springframework.http.server.reactive.HttpHandlerAdapterSupport
      • org.springframework.http.server.reactive.ReactorHttpHandlerAdapter (implements java.util.function.Function<T,R>)
      • org.springframework.http.server.reactive.RxNettyHttpHandlerAdapter (implements io.reactivex.netty.protocol.http.server.RequestHandler<I,O>)

      • org.springframework.http.server.reactive.UndertowHttpHandlerAdapter (implements io.undertow.server.HttpHandler)
    • reactor.core.publisher.Mono<T> (implements org.reactivestreams.Publisher<T>)
